21:T536,My responsibilities include:

• Planning and managing resources in our Azure environment
• Managing our Intune\MECM environment
• Security hardening for our Windows and Entra environments

Some highlights and accomplishments in this role:

• Migrated legacy GPOs to Intune policies - This enables us to have full Entra-joined workstations and   leverage autopilot to speed up the provisioning process

• Migrated workstation patching to Windows Update for Business - Allows for simplified management of OS patches for our workstation fleet as well as out-of-band patching.

• Fully revamped the workstation imaging process - Allows us to fully reimage machines without technicians onsite. Improves productivity by providing a rapid method to restore functionality to a computer

• Expanded our datacenter footprint into Azure - Building the structure for us to host in Azure improved our flexibility. We replaced a 5TB file server with a tiered storage solution in Azure which allowed us to save dramatically on our hosting costs. 

• Deployed Entra ID Governance - Entra ID governance with automated assignment policies allowed us to begin automating role-based access with access packages. We were able to use this in conjunction with BeyondTrust to provide more secure, zero-trust remote access for vendor accounts.c: [
